漢奸宣誓時侮辱中國人之後<br />\n整個議會一定要改變以免成反華辱華一個前哨站</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飲我地中國人既水<br />\n用我地中國人既地方<br />\n呼吸我地中國既空氣<br />\n有本事就滾唔好靠奶鳩我地中國人鞋底生存</blockquote><br />\n用海鷗啦你，用乜撚sony ，漢汗走狗"},{"pid":"199384243c921c315ab4ab82bcc155e062650a28","tid":503671,"uid":36157,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:11:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>根本擺明收左日本人美國人錢去搞事<br />\n自從俾兩條漢奸宣誓時侮辱中國人之後<br />\n整個議會一定要改變以免成反華辱華一個前哨站</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦撚樣&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n飲我地中國人既水<br />\n用我地中國人既地方<br />\n呼吸我地中國既空氣<br />\n有本事就滾唔好靠奶鳩我地中國人鞋底生存</blockquote><br />\n用海鷗啦你，用乜撚sony ，漢汗走狗</blockquote><br />\n條sony五毛講得岩。<br />\n死中囯暴政覇權侵略香港<br />\n中囯人滾出香港<br />\n<br />\nbtw，sony五毛再獲得0.50元。"},{"pid":"144e6696b2adb1bfbbeab22cf17deff125e37e12","tid":503671,"uid":7026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"影得幾好"},{"pid":"4ece89ad286b3a0581d4115fe17f6155d0b5e9d6","tid":503671,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:58:51.000Z","msg":"5毛貓其實有冇回應過點解要用外國牌子相機唔用國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e45eb77558400071cddc4633e9e73c2da1f17d5e","tid":503671,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5毛貓其實有冇回應過點解要用外國牌子相機唔用國貨&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji pixelated&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢係用國貨<br />\n佢用支那宗主國日本嘅牌子：索尼"},{"pid":"4a14caa9b5f28aa168c2f55a2b9e3b4f1942c28b","tid":503671,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:57:44.000Z","msg":"去同梁宗耀講啦"},{"pid":"e9067782d7ea64b370e4df56dfa8af67c0072be0","tid":503671,"uid":121247,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-1